room_title: Escape room "High Noon Heist" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: This was our first time attempting an escape, and had an amazing time. Very clever puzzles, well run and organized, and I will definitely do it again!

room_title: Escape room "High Noon Heist" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: We had so much fun! The theme was beautiful and we loved the "mission" style room. The staff was really helpful and fun as they acted the screen for us before we went to the room. Highly recommend escape rooms especially the one in the valley!

room_title: Escape room "High Noon Heist" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: Excellent experience. Great time had by all... nothing to complain about. Would highly recommend for a fun get together
